Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure is 120/80\Nand pulse rate is 92.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.23,0:00:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking out the bullet now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullet is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Removal complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.63,0:00:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We still need to repair\Nthe blood vessel walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sutures.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure is 128/72\Nand pulse rate is 88.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The anesthesia hasn't worn off yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to keep fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Boyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like your surgery was successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The mayor has died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh… I'm sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, that's easy for you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you who backed out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,from our surgical team.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's just the boy came in\Nbefore the mayor--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is that we had to cover\Nfor you after you backed out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,from the team without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! I--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You disrupted the teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to do the mayor's surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,according to the Director's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you ignored the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But Chief! I was--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A surgical operation can only succeed\Nwith trust between all team members.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:03:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You were not a team player.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have already reported to the Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This incident has harmed\Nour hospital's authority,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Director is very disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself for consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma,\Nthe boy's blood pressure is 114/82.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,His pulse rate is 84,\Nand his vital signs are all very stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Um… The surgery earlier was\Ntruly amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayor Roedecker,\Nwho collapsed at the retreat,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,passed away in the hospital earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Many citizens have heard the sad news
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and brought flowers to the city hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They are all there to pay respect\Nto the late mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Eisler Memorial Hospital,\Nwhere the mayor was operated on,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,has just held a press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayor Roedecker's cause of death is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,acute stroke caused by\Ninternal carotid artery occlusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite our best efforts,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the swelling\Nwas unfortunately far too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The city office says\Nit will begin working out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the succession plan as soon as possible…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to sleep…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is the news about the murder\Nof Mr. and Mrs. Liebert late last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As there were signs that the room\Nwas ransacked, a robbery is suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There is also a possibility\Nof political terrorism
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,as they were currently seeking asylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The police are investigating\Nboth possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Their son was shot in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Although his surgery was successful,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,he is still unconscious\Nand in critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is weather news.\NSun is expected for the whole country…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what will happen to that boy…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what'll happen to me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Reinhart in the ICU said
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that he can't sleep at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we prescribe\Nsome sleeping pills for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. In that case…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him a tablet of Halcion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been like this all day.\NI can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey.\N-Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Becker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Things aren't going well for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the Director penalize you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:07:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you already.\NIt's all politics in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you played your cards right,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you could have had great success\Nin the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you will join my side\Nfrom now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You will get your chance\Nto redeem yourself somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get some drinks and relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I am here to question
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the twin sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective, now is not the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She's missing from her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She walks out of her room\Nand wanders about the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ki…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Eisler Memorial Hospital has become\Na well-recognized
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and a leading medical facility\Nin this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It is all because of the excellent\Ndoctors here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to extend my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unfortunate that the mayor\Npassed away in our hospital last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But we did everything we could as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thankfully, the public has not changed\Ntheir perception of the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are the doctors who did\Neverything to save the mayor,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Boyer and Dr. Eisen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I read your paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the great work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I… I am very sorry about the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's all in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You only did what you thought was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Director…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, I would like to ask
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the Head of Neurosurgery\Nto say a few words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.\NI need to make a speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to welcome\Nthe newly appointed Head,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Boyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Director, what does this…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay in the hospital if you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can forget\Nabout any promotion as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot give any chance to someone\Nwho causes problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your surgical skills are good. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You can also give up on publishing\Nany academic papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Director, please wait!\NI have to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.97,0:10:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't write any reference letter\Nfor you, even if you want to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say goodbye to any ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The path you had planned as a doctor\Nis no longer possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Surgery is teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only with everyone's effort
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that we can save lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.02,0:11:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva, can you talk to your father for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I only followed the order\Nof the patients coming in
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to do the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the engagement ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Norden! Nice suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more beautiful than ever tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to Germany after I read\NDr. Heinemann's papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He had taken me under his wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I think of it, the papers\Nthat impressed me so much
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,must have been written by someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like what I had been doing for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.87,0:13:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that I was being used by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought that if I could\Nget to a high position,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I could do any research I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to advance as academic scholars\Nbefore we can save lives. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No! A doctor's priority is to save lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,After all,\Npeople's lives aren't created equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No! All lives are created equal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a doctor, just a money-grubber!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A man like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is better off dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I should thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for opening\Nmy eyes as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost everything to operate on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I went that far to bring you back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is Anna Liebert. Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, can you do something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She did witness her parents being\Nmurdered right in front of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Although she is not injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,she is suffering from amnesia\Ndue to extreme terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you delay questioning the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That is going to be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The victim is a high-ranking\Ngovernment official from East Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't handle this quickly,\Nthe guys from the BKA will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They always follow close behind
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and take credit from us state police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to take it slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let this girl meet her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If she feels safe,\Nher memory might come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I cannot agree\Nto such an unprofessional method.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, Dr. Tenma probably\Nwon't give his permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Johan's doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What else can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you in a daze?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:16:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You look pretty exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been busy with emergency operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they're overworking you\Nnow that you're demoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's fine.\NI'm more relieved now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I just got paged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still going to work\Nwhen you're so tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only hurting yourself\Nfor being so hardworking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all this, Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all the presents\Nand letters for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a mountain of them\Nin his sister's room as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of their parents have died\Nand they only have each other now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so the press reported this as a sob story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't even pay\Nfor the medical bills now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just troublesome for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This tear-jerking story is not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:17:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be publicity for the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That means these kids\Nare still useful to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ye… Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We can get the two of them together\Nand take a picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and then release it to the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The press have been looking for pictures\Nmany times already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a photo of the orphaned twins\Nunder the great care
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of our excellent hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But the doctor in charge is saying\Nthat it's still too early
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to let them see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the doctor in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to let that man\Nbe in that prominent position.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Get Dr. Tenma off the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to try a kind gift\Nfrom the concerned citizens?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Henkel, how are you feeling today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling much better because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon we can take out the stitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, you can be discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have to take a lot of rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Mrs. Henkel anticonvulsants\Nand antihypertensives regularly--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!\NWe let this girl meet with her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then… She screamed so loudly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Get her to her room.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Boyer, what are you doing\Nwith that camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to capture the moving moment\Nof them meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll release it to the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who gave you permission to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the doctor in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no longer Johan's doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,From today, I'll be his doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided that it's fine\Nfor them to see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't use…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't use these kids for publicity!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Director's order!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be better for you to stop\Ndefying his orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I saved that boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a duty to protect him\Nuntil he's healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that, but look at him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:20:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as he saw his sister,\Nhe held out his hand and cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's conscious and showing good signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That means the surgery\Nwas very successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, but your work is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to where you should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Damn you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"Director's order"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Chief's order"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all a bunch of money-grubbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Father? Are you in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.96,0:21:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, are you still here so late?\NWere you in a meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, are you in bed already?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.61,0:21:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys… are better off dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.89,0:23:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,CHAPTER 3\NMURDER CASE
